  "summary": "AWS Community Hero and Solution Architect at Alinma Bank with 17+ years of experience in IT and digital transformation. Ahmed specializes in cloud-native architecture for financial services, driving digital banking initiatives . I am leading three Arabic-language meetups in Riyadh — AWS, Amazon SageMaker, and Kubernetes — and has organized 45+ community events for AWS to grow and empower the cloud community across the MENA region. I am AWS and Kubernetes certified and passionate about making cloud knowledge accessible in Arabic.",
